128
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:29,940
Fortunately, the lotus leaves covered me.

129
00:07:31,550 --> 00:07:32,350
Otherwise...

130
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,890
If that's the case,

131
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,730
