132
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,430
so he returned to the tavern.

133
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:41,720
Did you see that person's face?

134
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,909
What are you doing?

135
00:07:56,909 --> 00:07:57,909
He just saved you!

136
00:08:00,990 --> 00:08:02,820
