157
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,430
He wants to...

158
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,350
He wants to kill

159
00:09:21,350 --> 00:09:22,550
all the people we save

160
00:09:23,210 --> 00:09:25,210
