167
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,040
Zhao Ruyi's wife?

168
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:48,710
Doesn't she live in the west?

169
00:09:49,310 --> 00:09:50,150
After Zhao Ruyi died,

170
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:51,210
